 <exercise id="fs-idm73610688"><problem id="fs-idm57687392">
   <para id="fs-idm24034400">Let <emphasis effect="italics">α</emphasis> = 0.05<newline/>
    Decision: ________<newline/>
    Conclusion (write out in a complete sentence.): ________</para></problem>
 </exercise><exercise id="eip-572"><problem id="eip-idp77356624">
<para id="eip-idp77356880">How did you know to test the variance instead of the mean?</para>
</problem>
